            <output id="analyticalSkillsOutput">Level 1: Understands basic PPC metrics and terminology.</output>
            <p id="analyticalSkillsDescription">Understands basic PPC metrics and terminology. Requires guidance in interpreting data.</p>
            <br>
            <label for="technicalProficiency"><b>Technical Proficiency:</b></label>
            <input type="range" id="technicalProficiency" name="technicalProficiency" min="1" max="10" value="1" oninput="updateOutput('technicalProficiency', 'technicalProficiencyOutput', 'technicalProficiencyDescription')" required>
            <output id="technicalProficiencyOutput">Level 1: Executes basic PPC campaign setup and optimization tasks.</output>
            <p id="technicalProficiencyDescription">Executes basic PPC campaign setup and optimization tasks. Requires guidance in using PPC platforms.</p>
